author_ssm: Megan O'Shea, Molly A. Cross, and Alexa Logush
unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Education Serials
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Collection of Education Serials contains over 200 titles on education in the United States (US) and other countries.  The collection dates between 1883 and 2016, with the bulk of the material dating from the 1940s through the 1980s.  Topics include elementary, high school, and college level education and curricula; student organizations; cultural institutions; and professional organizations related to education.
